Sentencas: Solid oxide fuel cell (SOFC) is regarded as an environmentally friendly energy conversion device, which can directly convert the chemical energy stored in the fuel to the electrical energy.
Titulo: Utilizing High Entropy Effects for Developing Chromium-Tolerance Cobalt-Free Cathode for Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: However, the degradation of cathodes caused by Cr-containing steel interconnects is a major problem that limits the broader application of SOFC.
Titulo: Utilizing High Entropy Effects for Developing Chromium-Tolerance Cobalt-Free Cathode for Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: Herein, a novel A-site high entropy oxide, based on the cobalt-free PrBaFe2O5+& delta; (PBF) cathode, La0.2Pr0.2Nd0.2Sm0.2Gd0.2BaFe2O5+& delta; (LPNSGBF), is proposed as a high catalyst activity and Cr-tolerance cathode for SOFC.
Titulo: Utilizing High Entropy Effects for Developing Chromium-Tolerance Cobalt-Free Cathode for Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: The anode-supported cell with the LPNSGBF cathode exhibits an excellent peak power density of 1020.69 mW cm(-2) at 800 & DEG;C, which is better than that of the PBF (794.96 mW cm(-2)).
Titulo: Utilizing High Entropy Effects for Developing Chromium-Tolerance Cobalt-Free Cathode for Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: Moreover, under the Cr-containing atmosphere, the outstanding stability of the single cell with the LPNSGBF for 100 h with a degradation rate of 0.17% h(-1), is much lower than the 0.79% h(-1) for that of the PBF cathode.
Titulo: Utilizing High Entropy Effects for Developing Chromium-Tolerance Cobalt-Free Cathode for Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: The study provides a new strategy for achieving the enhanced oxygen reduction reaction and high Cr-tolerance of the cobalt-free cathode by high entropy doping.
Titulo: Utilizing High Entropy Effects for Developing Chromium-Tolerance Cobalt-Free Cathode for Solid Oxide Fuel Cells
